You can also specify a hook to fire on all events:

```elixir
model =
  Axon.input("data")
  |> Axon.dense(8)
  |> Axon.attach_hook(&IO.inspect/1, on: :all)
  |> Axon.relu()
  |> Axon.dense(1)

{init_fn, predict_fn} = Axon.build(model)
```

